title: Pixel 3a XL Unable to Be Turned On, Repeatedly buzzing. Power button has no effect.
content:
My phone was regrettably run through the washing machine. It's been dried in a bag of rice, and is currently dry. Every second or so it emits a "buzz--buzz" which I can do nothing about. The power button does nothing. Occasionally the buzzing will stop for a second, change in pitch, and then resume as "normal". 

Ideally there is a way to turn it on and fix this.
